title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 85-1.5 - Determination of noncompliance

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 85-1.5 - Determination of noncompliance

State Regulations

If any NOI or application filed pursuant to section
85-1.2 or
85-1.3
of this Subpart fails to
comply in whole or in part with the applicable provisions of the Public Service

Law and these regulations, the commission or its designee will, within 14 days
of receipt, advise the applicant of the noncompliance and how to
comply. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16
§§
85-1.5

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
